Description: Sherd of handle of Cypriot basket handled pottery amphora. The handle rises from the shoulder and turns to the left. Inscription on handle.
Curator's comments: A. Johnston, 'Fragmenta Britannica II. Sherds from Naukratis.' BICS 29 (1982) 36, no.8.
Bibliographic references: Bernand 1970 / Le Delta égyptien d'après les textes grecs, i: les confins libyques (p. 683, no. 415)
Johnston 2006b / The Delta: From Gamma to Zeta (p. 26 fig. 14, p. 29 Table 1)
Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JA.074)
